<i>adverb</i>: 처참히 [처ː참히], 무참히 [무참히], 곤고히 [곤ː고히] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>처참히 [처ː참히]</dt><br>
<dd>miserably; wretchedly</dd><br>
<dd>몹시 무서워 떨릴 정도로 슬프고 끔찍하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Sadly and dreadfully to such a degree that one trembles out of fear.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>무참히 [무참히]</dt><br>
<dd>cruelly; miserably</dd><br>
<dd>매우 끔찍하고 비참하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Very horribly and tragically.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>곤고히 [곤ː고히]</dt><br>
<dd>miserably; wretchedly</dd><br>
<dd>형편이나 처지 등이 딱하고 어렵게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a state that one's situation or condition is miserable and hard.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>